- **Application**: This market can also be segmented based on application areas, including food and beverage, pharmaceuticals, automotive, e-commerce, and others. Different industries have unique packaging requirements, and automation solutions can be customized to meet these specific needs.
- **End User**: The end-user segment of the packaging automation market includes manufacturers, contract packagers, and logistics companies. Each of these end users has distinct demands when it comes to packaging automation, and the market caters to each of these segments with tailored solutions.

